jalse.misc

Class JALSEExceptions

  • java.lang.Object
    • jalse.misc.JALSEExceptions

  • public final class JALSEExceptions
extends java.lang.Object
    These are the suppliers for all the common specific exceptions JALSE throws. JALSE currently does not provide any custom exception types but instead uses the suitable java.lang exceptions.
    Author:
    Elliot Ford
